<p class="indent1" style="-uslm-lc:I12" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">Except as otherwise provided in this subsection, property shall be classified under the following table:<table id="id6757ce1d-56ce-11e9-b43f-92f716297fbc" style="border-collapse:collapse; border=0;  -uslm-lc: c2,L0,tp0,p7,7/8,s10,xs102,tp0,p7,7/8,s10,xs102; " width="50%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><colgroup><col style="min-width: 100pt;"/><col style="width:106pt ; max-width:106pt;"/></colgroup><thead><tr class="header" style="font-size:7pt;-uslm-lc:h1;"><th style="min-width: 100.0pt; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;"><p style=" text-align:left;"><b>Property shall be treated     as:</b></p></th><th style="width:106.0pt ; max-width:106.0pt; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;"><p style=" text-align:left;"><b>If such property has a class   life (in years) of:</b></p></th></tr></thead><tbody style="line-height:8pt; font-size:7pt;"><tr style="-uslm-lc:I02;"><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><p class="leaders" style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:2em;"><span>3-year property</span></p></td><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:5em;">4 or less</p></td></tr><tr style="-uslm-lc:I02;"><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><p class="leaders" style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:2em;"><span>5-year property</span></p></td><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:5em;">More than 4 but less than 10</p></td></tr><tr style="-uslm-lc:I02;"><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><p class="leaders" style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:2em;"><span>7-year property</span></p></td><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:5em;">10 or more but less than 16</p></td></tr><tr style="-uslm-lc:I02;"><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><p class="leaders" style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:2em;"><span>10-year property</span></p></td><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:5em;">16 or more but less than 20</p></td></tr><tr style="-uslm-lc:I02;"><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><p class="leaders" style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:2em;"><span>15-year property</span></p></td><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:5em;">20 or more but less than 25</p></td></tr><tr style="-uslm-lc:I02;"><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-right:2pt;"><p class="leaders" style=" text-align:left; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:2em;"><span>20-year property</span></p></td><td style=" text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left: 2pt;"><p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent: -1em; padding-left:5em;">25 or more.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>
</p>
